  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Assistance - Country-Level Funding - IOM 2020</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The continued high level of displacements, the increasing number of people without access to basic services, ongoing violence and inter-community tensions, Ebola Virus Disease (EVD) outbreak in Eastern Democratic Republic of the Congo, and recently COVID-19 crisis puts extreme pressure on humanitarian delivery systems. This project aims to contribute towards a more informed and coordinated humanitarian response in displacement sites in Ituri and North Kivu provinces, as well as to improve the living conditions and protection of the most vulnerable IDPs.</narrative>
  </description>
